					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/CRE_Main_A\r\n- Use ReCon command \"oe MonkAmulet_Get\" and equip the amulet.\r\n- Approach the statue of Lathander in the Creche: S_CRE_MonkAmulet_StatueBanter_f83fe070-3bae-4996-a349-7e14f0a0573a\r\n\"goto 75 9 62\""
