				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The spirit inside the Sentient Amulet, once a monk of Lathander, sees a statue of Lathander in the interior courtyard of the Gith Creche, once a Lathander monastery. Pilgrims of old used to visit the statue to see a holy relic - the Blood of Lathander - though unbeknownst to them, it was a fake prop. The Mad Monk reminisces about his own pilgrimage."
				}
			}
